The files in this directory are derived from the PQClean project:
    https://github.com/PQClean/PQClean
    crypto_kem/ml-kem-768/clean  and  common/

PQClean's ML-KEM (Kyber) clean reference implementation is released into the
public domain (CC0 1.0 Universal). Where individual upstream files carry a
license header, that header is retained.

Local modifications in this fork:
  - fips202.c replaced by a compact in-tree Keccak (../keccak.c)
  - all sources compiled as a single amalgamation via ../mlkem768.c
  - randombytes routed to the library's getrandom()-based PRNG
